<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .badge { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
    .price-new { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #16a34a; }
    .price-old { font-size: 18px; color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: line-through; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #16a34a; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 16px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Hey 👋</p>
  <p>Good news! An item on your watchlist just dropped below your target price.</p>

  <% if @product.image_url.present? %>
    <img src="<%= @product.image_url %>" alt="" style="max-height: 180px; object-fit: contain; margin: 16px 0;" />
  <% end %>

  <h2 style="margin: 8px 0;"><%= @product.name %></h2>

  <p>
    <span class="price-new">$<%= @product.price %></span>
    <% if @product.old_price.present? %>
      &nbsp;<span class="price-old">$<%= @product.old_price %></span>
    <% end %>
    <% if @product.discount.present? && @product.discount > 0 %>
      &nbsp;<span class="badge">-<%= @product.discount %>% OFF</span>
    <% end %>
  </p>

  <p>Your target was: <strong>$<%= @alert.target_price %></strong></p>

  <a href="<%= @product.store_url %>" class="btn">View Deal →</a>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>You set this alert on ozvfy.com. This alert has now been marked as triggered.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
